### _sp_sv_limit_userinfo_change

_sp_sv_limit_userinfo_change

Limit number of userinfo changes (name, skin, rate, ...). Clients who change their userinfo too often will see a warning message and new changes will be ignored.

Values:

- 0: No limit (default)
- 1: Limit
